Privacy Policy for Child Growth Tracker Pro App

Last updated: 27th August 2023

1. Introduction

Welcome to Child Growth Tracker Pro! This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application Child Growth Tracker Pro (the "App"). Please read this Privacy Policy carefully. If you do not agree with the terms of this Privacy Policy, please do not access or use the App.

2. Information We Collect

Since this app is about child growth tracking, we collect the following information about your child, and this information is exclusively stored on your local device:
- Your child's name, gender, date of birth and their picture(optional).
- Height, weight, and head circumference measurements over time.

No other data is collected.

3. How We Use Your Information

We may use the information we collect for various purposes, including:
- Providing meaningful insights into children's growth.
- Monitoring and analyzing usage and trends.

4. Disclosure of Your Information

We do not share your information with any third parties. All data is stored only on your local device.

5. Your Choices

You have the right to:
- Update or correct your information.
- Delete your data.

6. Security

As your data is stored locally on your device, it remains properly secured.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at calidaddeveloper@gmail.com.

By using the App, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
